body_html:
#MeToo
Compiled TF 1.7 (Ubuntu 16.04) today with mkl, trying to run custom seq2seq with attention made out of tf.contib's seq2seq building blocks, got:
2018-04-06 21:52:38.076967: F ./tensorflow/core/util/mkl_util.h:1288] Non-OK-status: Status(error::Code::INVALID_ARGUMENT, "Unsupported data format") status: Invalid argument: Unsupported data format
There is no even message about what OP caused failure. Seq2seq is batch-major if important.
